snippet.title: The Reality of Amber heard, Elon Musk and Cara Delevinge Three Way Affair
snippet.description:
In this video, we’ll talk about the reality of Amber Heard, Elon Musk, and Cara Delevinge Three Way Affair.

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE: http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
___________________________________________

Tesla CEO Elon Musk has denied having a "three-way affair" with his ex Amber Heard and model Cara Delevingne. During a deposition in Johnny Depp's lawsuit against his ex-wife Amber Heard, it was alleged by one of the actress' friends that she had spent the night with Elon Musk and their friend Cara Delevingne back in November 2016.

However, Elon Musk has now not only denied the claims, but also his involvement with the Aquaman star during her marriage with Johnny Depp.
